# SoilUnitAnalysis — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in real values.
# Per CLAUDE.md "Hard Rules": credentials must be read from environment
# variables; never hard-code them in scripts.

# NEON personal access token. Recommended for `neonUtilities` calls so AOP
# downloads are not subject to anonymous rate limits.
# Obtain from https://data.neonscience.org/ after creating an account.
NEON_TOKEN=
